ou will have seen the scale of some of the figures that have been talked about in terms of the impact on the HE sector at this time. Clearly, a four-nation approach to that will be crucial.&#10;Speaker: Suzy Davies AM&#10;Content: Thank you.&#10;Speaker: Lynne Neagle AM&#10;Content: Okay. Thank you. Well, we have come to the end of our time, and, as">
