n their study arrangements due to the pandemic.&#10;4. A four-nation approach will be crucial in addressing the impact on the HE sector, as significant figures have been discussed regarding the potential impact of the pandemic on higher education.&#10;5. Wales' universities are part of the Universities UK group that formed the principles for schools and FE colleges, and while universities are independent institutions, the Welsh Government is working with representatives of the HE sector to keep them apprised of the situation and discuss possible similar measures.">
